<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <title>Your Order Has Shipped</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; background: #f9f9f9; margin: 0; padding: 0;">
  <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: #fff; padding: 32px;">

    <h2 style="color: #1a6bb5; margin-top: 0;">Your Order Is On Its Way!</h2>
    <p>Great news — your order <strong>#{{orderNumber}}</strong> has been shipped.</p>

    <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 16px 0 24px;">
      <tr>
        <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #eee; font-weight: bold; width: 40%;">Carrier</td>
        <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #eee;">{{carrier}}</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #eee; font-weight: bold;">Tracking Number</td>
        <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #eee; font-family: monospace;">{{trackingNumber}}</td>
      </tr>
    </table>

    <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #eee; margin: 24px 0;" />
    <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #999; margin: 0;">
      Questions? Contact us at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}" style="color: #007bff;">{{supportEmail}}</a><br>
      © {{year}} {{appName}}
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
